title: Interstate 82 Starter Pack
description:
_StarSky pack Info_
Installation Instructions
If on a 64bit system
Extract the .zip into your C:Program Files (x86)
After extracting just go ahead and run the bf1942.exe
Search for a server in multiplayer for interstate 1982 example is82.com and join and your in!
